HEADWORD: nineties
<hw>nineties</hw> <pos>n. pl.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The decade from
1890 to 1899; <as>as, the gay <ex>nineties</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The decade from 1990 to 1999; <as>as, they spent a
ton of money to solve the Y2K bug in the
<ex>nineties</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The time of life between ages 90 and 100.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mid-nineties.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ninetieth</ent>⟦br⟧
